    tldr: "Discover Rome's best affordable neighborhoods for expats beyond touristy areas. From vibrant San Lorenzo to bohemian Testaccio, learn where to find authentic Roman life without the tourist prices.",
    metaDescription: "Best cheap neighborhoods in Rome for expats. Discover affordable areas with local culture, restaurants, and real Roman living away from tourists.",
    keywords: ["best neighborhoods Rome expats", "cheap areas Rome", "affordable Rome neighborhoods", "where to live Rome", "expat neighborhoods Rome", "budget Rome living"],
    image: "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552832860-cfb67165eaf0?w=1200",
