    metaDescription: "Summer Rome survival guide: dealing with heat, August ferragosto closures, and tourist crowds for expats living in Rome",
    keywords: ["summer in Rome", "Rome August", "Rome heat survival", "ferragosto Rome", "August closures Rome"],
