    "tldr": "Discover Rome's bike sharing ecosystem: Mobilità Nuova, Lime, and dockless options. Learn pricing, coverage zones, user experiences, and integration with other transport modes.",
    "metaDescription": "Rome bike sharing guide: Mobike, Lime, and municipal systems. How to use, pricing, coverage maps, and comparing sharing vs. ownership for expats.",
